{"markdown":{"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"::: {.question}\n\n**Momentum Long–Short**\n\n\n```{r}\n#| eval: true\n#| echo: false\n#| results: asis\nlibrary(webexercises)\n\nset.seed(101)\nRw       <- round(runif(1, 0.12, 0.40), 2)  # winners next-period return (decimal)\nRl       <- round(runif(1, -0.05, 0.18), 2) # losers next-period return (decimal)\nbeta_LS  <- round(runif(1, -0.10, 0.20), 2) # beta of the long-short (often near zero)\nrf       <- round(runif(1, 0.02, 0.05), 2)\nmrp      <- round(runif(1, 0.04, 0.08), 2)\n\nspread    <- Rw - Rl\ncapm_req  <- rf + beta_LS * mrp\nalpha     <- spread - capm_req\n\nspread_pct <- round(100*spread, 2)\ncapm_pct   <- round(100*capm_req, 2)\nalpha_pct  <- round(100*alpha, 2)\n```\n\nA momentum strategy buys past **winners** and shorts **losers** (equal weights). Next period: winners return **`r round(100*Rw,2)`%**, losers return **`r round(100*Rl,2)`%**; the strategy beta is **β = `r beta_LS`**.  \nAssume **R<sub>f</sub> = `r round(100*rf,2)`%**, **MRP = `r round(100*mrp,2)`%**.\n\n::: {.question-block}\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n  <label for=\"module5_num_q5a\"><strong>5a. Long–short return (in %):</strong></label>\n  <input type=\"number\" id=\"module5_num_q5a\" name=\"module5_num_q5a\" style=\"width:200px;\"\n         data-correct-answer=`r spread_pct` data-tolerance=\"0.05\" step=\"0.01\" />\n</form>\n\n<div id=\"feedback-module5_num_q5a\" class=\"feedback\" data-status=\"\" style=\"display:none;\">\n✅ <strong>Long–short return</strong><br>\nSpread = E[R]<sub>winners</sub> − E[R]<sub>losers</sub> = `r round(100*Rw,2)`% − `r round(100*Rl,2)`% =\n<strong>`r spread_pct`%</strong>.\n</div>\n:::\n\n::: {.question-block}\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n  <label for=\"module5_num_q5b\"><strong>5b. CAPM required return for this portfolio (in %):</strong></label>\n  <input type=\"number\" id=\"module5_num_q5b\" name=\"module5_num_q5b\" style=\"width:260px;\"\n         data-correct-answer=`r capm_pct` data-tolerance=\"0.05\" step=\"0.01\" />\n</form>\n\n<div id=\"feedback-module5_num_q5b\" class=\"feedback\" data-status=\"\" style=\"display:none;\">\n✅ <strong>CAPM required return</strong><br>\nE[R]<sub>CAPM</sub> = R<sub>f</sub> + β × MRP = `r round(100*rf,2)`% + (`r beta_LS`) × `r round(100*mrp,2)`% =\n<strong>`r capm_pct`%</strong>.  \nWhen β is near zero, CAPM says the expected long–short return should be close to the risk‑free rate.\n</div>\n:::\n\n::: {.question-block}\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n  <label for=\"module5_num_q5c\"><strong>5c. Alpha (in %):</strong></label>\n  <input type=\"number\" id=\"module5_num_q5c\" name=\"module5_num_q5c\" style=\"width:200px;\"\n         data-correct-answer=`r alpha_pct` data-tolerance=\"0.05\" step=\"0.01\" />\n</form>\n\n<div id=\"feedback-module5_num_q5c\" class=\"feedback\" data-status=\"\" style=\"display:none;\">\n✅ <strong>Alpha</strong><br>\nα = Realized long–short return − CAPM required = `r spread_pct`% − `r capm_pct`% =\n<strong>`r alpha_pct`%</strong>.<br>\nIf α &gt; 0 with β ≈ 0, momentum delivers returns not explained by market β → evidence of a factor or behavioral effect.\n</div>\n:::\n\n\n:::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"knitr"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"kee